spanGrp.span: ino kümsü ake, kutolo ye ayi bidi pungu qhalo shi aghi nani.
as far as I can recall it must have happened around 4 and 5

u.seg: ino kümsü ake kutolo ye ayi bidi [a] pungu qhalo shi aghi nani

spanGrp.span: did not know the earthquake come but
iza no pano ithi puzüno, küda kelono, ithughi lu ipuzü,
my mother knew and could get up when she wake (me) up

u.seg: iza no pano ithi puzüno küda kelono ithughi lu ipuzü

spanGrp.span: tisheno tishi earthquake ighi keu tiye,
and after that, like that earthquake coming
ighono clear shi ku shi kelo mu, mtha va, ighono msah pu, ngo akeu lei.
not very clear about what (I) did, was very scared and staying

u.seg: ighono (clear) shi ku shi kelo mu mtha va, ighono msah pu ngo akeu lei

spanGrp.span: kemu qeti shi pu, tisheno ningu atsünipu akucho pu, küda tishi pu,
but then after that woke up all us sisters

u.seg: kemu qeti shi pu tisheno ningu atsünipu akucho pu küda tishi pu

spanGrp.span: ipu tisheno tipau no khala chiu no ipeu noqo küda.
and after that woke up my brothers from outside

u.seg: ipu tisheno [ü] tipau no khala chiu no ipeu noqo küda

spanGrp.span: ipu tishi pu, tisheno ningu qo ye tishi va, aa lakhi lo ngo pu,
and after that and then we all stayed at one place

u.seg: ipu tishi pu tisheno ningu qo ye tishi va [ü] aa lakhi lo ngo pu

spanGrp.span: akighini shi tishi pu, tisheno ipe ngo ake.

u.seg: akighini shi tishi pu tisheno [ü] ipe ngo ake

spanGrp.span: kümsü kelo, kitila tishive pu, tinguno alau ye kühave.
if (we) recall, happened for a while and beyond that (was) not there

u.seg: kümsü kelo kitila tishive pu tinguno alau ye kühave
